5.1 vmpc-action-alist
=====================

The `vmpc-action-alist' variable controls which actions are performed
if various conditions are met when creating a reply.  Its format is
something like this:

     '(  ("condition 1" "action 1" "action 2")
         ("condition 2" "action 3")
         ...                         )

If you do not want to set all the other alists then sent this one as it
will be used as a fall back.


