6.1 vmpc-auto-profiles-file
===========================

The variable `vmpc-auto-profiles-file' contains the name of the file
used for saving profiles when `vmpc-prompt-for-profile' is used with a
non-nil argument (see *note The vmpc-actions variable:: and *note
